{"id": "1255936367058354349", "channel_id": "1255885949964124300", "type": 0, "author_id": "484555315447332864", "author_name": "randomplayer852", "author_bot": false, "content": "克系本身還是歐美那邊比較火吧，COC，DND都玩地比較多。再加上港澳台那邊玩家基數就少。上steam我覺得還是蠻有希望能火的。", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T17:22:44.076000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255885949964124300", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "到底有沒有新常駐模式", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
