{"id": "1255715338025435146", "channel_id": "1255715338025435146", "type": 0, "author_id": "1205711780932755476", "author_name": "0120_cccc", "author_bot": false, "content": "這邊用了一次復活也打不過，甚至把卡都抽完了（沒得打），配隊是24、珈倫、環行拉蒙娜和莉莉，想問問是配隊的問題還是說有其他方法打過呢？謝謝🙏🙏", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T02:44:26.648000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1255715338188881930", "filename": "Screenshot_20240627_103252__Morimens.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 151917, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255715338025435146/1255715338188881930/Screenshot_20240627_103252__Morimens.jpg?ex=69cc868a&is=69cb350a&hm=45f3db3d006fc07d3d649f9003ade6d18d1719effc3161e6dc8950a12d9ac1b4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255715338025435146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "3-13應該怎麼打？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1255716489906884709", "channel_id": "1255715338025435146", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "3-13是啥？希洛異化成BOSS？\n如果是，那麼，建議用四小強吧，別對啥SSR有崇高信仰，本遊戲對理解，是比較重要的。\n好了，回到主題，BOSS要怎麼打，首先，關卡中，要拿鏡像，給不定壁壘，等價交換，這樣在燒牌回合，你就能輕鬆撐住，如果還不理解，就自己去試用看看吧...", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T02:49:01.278000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255715338025435146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "3-13應該怎麼打？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1255717001083617340", "channel_id": "1255715338025435146", "type": 0, "author_id": "1205711780932755476", "author_name": "0120_cccc", "author_bot": false, "content": "是的！謝謝你我會試試的！", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T02:51:03.152000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255715338025435146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "3-13應該怎麼打？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1255717066485399594", "channel_id": "1255715338025435146", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "BOSS會有幾回合把你的手牌全部上消耗，\n這時候不要隨便出牌，避免到後面沒有優質牌可以打，\n這回合可以打環拉複製出的牌(本來就會消耗沒差)，以及用24的狂氣來輸出\n記得覺醒24、多用狂氣來打傷害，\n亂打牌讓牌被這隻王吃光的話很容易就後繼無力", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T02:51:18.745000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255715338025435146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "3-13應該怎麼打？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
