{"id": "1255717335814373448", "channel_id": "1255715338025435146", "type": 0, "author_id": "676337286769672192", "author_name": "hailananxie7110", "author_bot": false, "content": "附贈個人常用的隊伍圖，四小強，其實真的沒有弱多少(確實比較弱是肯定的)", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T02:52:22.958000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1255717335579365527", "filename": "Screenshot_2024.06.27_10.51.22.186.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 992001, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255715338025435146/1255717335579365527/Screenshot_2024.06.27_10.51.22.186.png?ex=69cc8866&is=69cb36e6&hm=b5e43c1de4a84bfae708afb4242bac0106d9098bf8008e68a6920d34daa041cb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255715338025435146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "3-13應該怎麼打？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
