{"id": "1255768783138590792", "channel_id": "1255715338025435146", "type": 0, "author_id": "1164258265799086080", "author_name": "metam0n", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T06:16:48.956000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1255768782933327882", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2384166, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1255715338025435146/1255768782933327882/image.png?ex=69cc0f90&is=69cabe10&hm=778248f24b0500afe836eefabb420b3a7b4893e614e5a260e3aacff019a35469&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255715338025435146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "3-13應該怎麼打？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1255769495755161670", "channel_id": "1255715338025435146", "type": 0, "author_id": "1164258265799086080", "author_name": "metam0n", "author_bot": false, "content": "1.可以参考其他玩家给出的地图和事件选项透视，推荐拿到「☆美好回忆☆」和「☆银白差分机☆」。\n\n2.首领战需要注意机制说明，看屏幕中上方的滚动条或者点击首领查看意图。重点是「溶解」机制，牌打完了就没了。\n\n3.需要复活或者死亡抵抗的帮助，那么推荐携带命轮「惩戒」、「希冀」、周年庆命轮「极夜与破晓」。", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T06:19:38.857000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255715338025435146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "3-13應該怎麼打？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1255855100992163880", "channel_id": "1255715338025435146", "type": 0, "author_id": "1048205315201581156", "author_name": "tourin.", "author_bot": false, "content": "主要問題應該還是在平均等級太低吧，我想技能等級可能也沒到都是4，你需要每天分配一定數量銀鑰去換靈啡肽，然後換物資升技能和升等，而不是全拿去抽角，初期開始玩如果不克金就需要耐著性子去存物資升級升技能還有祕契，有多才拿去抽角和命輪(第四章開始沒命輪會打的很磨耗)。\n我完全沒課金，第77天融災也能打到325，加油", "timestamp": "2024-06-27T11:59:48.736000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1255715338025435146", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "3-13應該怎麼打？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
